Prawn Dipping Sauces | Photo – RecipeTin Eats This prawn sauce is packed with veggies. This delicious side dish is ready in a couple of minutes once the chopping is out of the way. This can be served with any preference of your choice. Prawns can be the ideal food option for weight loss too. Ingredients Prawn sauce | Photo – GoodtoKnow Method To clean prawns, start by rinsing them in cold water. Next, hold the body of the prawn with one hand and cut off the head using your other hand. Then, pull off the tail, peel away the outer shell, and pull off the legs from the underside of the shell. Method